@startuml
!theme plain
title Excel 批量导入和批量编辑异步时序图

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam ParticipantPadding 18
skinparam BoxPadding 10

skinparam participant {
  BackgroundColor #f4f4f4
  BorderColor #2c3e50
  FontStyle bold
  FontColor #2c3e50
}

skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor #eef6ff
  BorderColor #2c3e50
  FontColor #2c3e50
}

skinparam collections {
  BackgroundColor #f9f9f9
  BorderColor #2c3e50
  FontColor #2c3e50
}

skinparam queue {
  BackgroundColor #fff7e6
  BorderColor #8a5a00
  FontColor #5c3b00
}

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #fff8dc
  BorderColor #d4ac0d
  FontColor #333333
}

skinparam sequence {
  GroupBackgroundColor #f9f9f9
  GroupBodyBackgroundColor #ffffff
  GroupBorderColor #3498db
  GroupFontColor #2c3e50
  GroupHeaderFontColor #2c3e50
}

actor "Merchant / Ops" as merchant
participant "Upload API" as api #e8f4f9
participant "OSS / USS" as filestore #eef6ff
database "product_supply_task" as taskdb #eef6ff
database "product_supply_task_item" as itemdb #eef6ff
participant "Parser Worker" as parser #fdf2e9
participant "Item Worker" as itemworker #e8f8f5
database "product_supply_staging" as stagingdb #eef6ff
participant "Risk Engine / QC Builder" as risk #f9ebea
queue "QC Review Item" as qcqueue #fff7e6
participant "Publish Worker" as publish #eafaf1
database "Formal Item Table" as itemtable #eef6ff
queue "Outbox / DLQ" as outbox #fff7e6
participant "Error File / Report Generator" as report #fdf2e9

== 1. 提交任务 ==
merchant -> api: 1. 上传 Excel / 批量提交
activate api
api -> filestore: 2. 上传源文件到 OSS / USS
activate filestore
filestore --> api: input_file_ref / file_name / hash
deactivate filestore

api -> taskdb: 3. 创建 product_supply_task\nstatus=PENDING, execution_mode=ASYNC,\ninput_file_ref / file_name / input_file_hash
activate taskdb
taskdb --> api: task_id
deactivate taskdb
api --> merchant: 4. 返回 task_id
deactivate api

note right of api
批量链路按“任务 + 行级明细 + 暂存快照 + 错误文件 + 补偿”设计，
不能把整个 Excel 读入内存后直接循环写正式表。
end note

== 2. Parser Worker ==
parser -> taskdb: 5. CAS 抢占任务\nPENDING -> PARSING
activate parser
activate taskdb
taskdb --> parser: claim ok
deactivate taskdb

parser -> taskdb: 6. 读取文件元数据\n校验 input_file_ref / hash / 模板版本 / 列结构
activate taskdb
taskdb --> parser: file metadata
deactivate taskdb

parser -> filestore: 6.1 按 input_file_ref 读取源文件
activate filestore
filestore --> parser: file stream
deactivate filestore

loop 7. 流式解析文件，每 N 行一批
  parser -> parser: 7.1 stream read\n不能一次性加载到内存
  parser -> itemdb: 7.2 batch insert task items
  activate itemdb
  itemdb --> parser: inserted
  deactivate itemdb

  parser -> taskdb: 7.3 update parsed_count\nparse_checkpoint / heartbeat_at
  activate taskdb
  taskdb --> parser: updated
  deactivate taskdb
end

parser -> taskdb: 8. 写 total_count\nPARSING -> RUNNING
activate taskdb
taskdb --> parser: updated
deactivate taskdb
deactivate parser

note right of parser
parse_checkpoint 示例:
{
  "sheet": "Sheet1",
  "row_no": 12000,
  "byte_offset": 8842211
}

工程上可先转规范化 CSV / JSONL，
再按 offset 恢复；否则按 row_no 快速跳过。
end note

note right of itemdb
幂等兜底:
UNIQUE(task_id, item_no)
UNIQUE(task_id, idempotency_key)
end note

== 3. Item Worker ==
loop 9. 扫描小批量 item
  itemworker -> itemdb: 9.1 SELECT ...\nstatus IN (PENDING, FAILED)\nnext_retry_at <= NOW()\nLIMIT 500
  activate itemworker
  activate itemdb
  itemdb --> itemworker: pending rows
  deactivate itemdb

  group 每个 item / 小批次独立事务
    itemworker -> itemdb: 9.2 CAS item -> NORMALIZING
    activate itemdb
    itemdb --> itemworker: claim ok
    deactivate itemdb

    itemworker -> itemworker: 9.3 读取 raw_row_ref\n按类目模板标准化
    itemworker -> itemdb: 9.4 写 normalized_ref
    activate itemdb
    itemdb --> itemworker: saved
    deactivate itemdb

    itemworker -> itemworker: 9.5 Schema / 主数据 /\n商品模型 / 交易契约校验

    alt 校验通过
      itemworker -> stagingdb: 9.6 写 product_supply_staging
      activate stagingdb
      stagingdb --> itemworker: staging_ref
      deactivate stagingdb

      itemworker -> stagingdb: 9.7 与线上 publish_version 做 Diff
      activate stagingdb
      stagingdb --> itemworker: diff result
      deactivate stagingdb

      itemworker -> risk: 9.8 生成 product_change_request
      activate risk

      alt 低风险自动准入
        risk -> publish: 9.9 enqueue publish candidate
        activate publish
        publish --> risk: queued
        deactivate publish
        risk -> itemdb: 9.10 item.status = APPROVED
        activate itemdb
        itemdb --> risk: updated
        deactivate itemdb
      else 高风险进入 QC
        risk -> qcqueue: 9.9 create product_qc_review_item
        activate qcqueue
        qcqueue --> risk: created
        deactivate qcqueue
        risk -> itemdb: 9.10 item.status = QC_PENDING
        activate itemdb
        itemdb --> risk: updated
        deactivate itemdb
      end

      deactivate risk
    else 校验失败
      itemworker -> itemdb: 9.6 item.status = FAILED\nerror_code / error_message
      activate itemdb
      itemdb --> itemworker: updated
      deactivate itemdb
    end
  end

  deactivate itemworker
end

note right of itemworker
不要用一个大事务包住 500 行。
否则一行失败会拖垮整批，
也会造成长事务和锁等待。
end note

== 4. QC / 发布 / 补偿 ==
alt QC 审核通过 或 自动准入
  publish -> itemtable: 10. 发布正式商品表\n写 payload / publish_version
  activate publish
  activate itemtable
  itemtable --> publish: published
  deactivate itemtable

  publish -> outbox: 11. 写 Outbox 事件
  activate outbox
  outbox --> publish: queued
  deactivate outbox

  publish -> itemdb: 12. 回写 item.status=PUBLISHED
  activate itemdb
  itemdb --> publish: updated
  deactivate itemdb

  publish -> taskdb: 13. 聚合 task progress / success_count
  activate taskdb
  taskdb --> publish: updated
  deactivate taskdb
  deactivate publish
else 驳回 / 发布失败 / 重试耗尽
  publish -> outbox: 10. 写 DLQ / compensation event
  activate publish
  activate outbox
  outbox --> publish: queued
  deactivate outbox

  publish -> report: 11. 生成错误文件 / 质量报告
  activate report
  report --> publish: error_file_ref / report_ref
  deactivate report

  publish -> taskdb: 11.1 回写 error_file_ref /\nreport_ref / error_file_name
  activate taskdb
  taskdb --> publish: updated
  deactivate taskdb

  publish -> itemdb: 12. 回写 item.status=FAILED 或 REJECTED
  activate itemdb
  itemdb --> publish: updated
  deactivate itemdb

  publish -> taskdb: 13. 聚合 failed_count / rejected_count
  activate taskdb
  taskdb --> publish: updated
  deactivate taskdb
  deactivate publish
end

note over parser,itemworker
好处:
1. 解析失败不会污染正式商品表
2. 行级失败不会拖垮整批任务
3. 发布和下游刷新可以限速、重试和补偿
end note

@enduml
